SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(DocEntry),SUM(DocTotal) from orpc WITH (NOLOCK) where (CardCode = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') and (DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and ISNULL(U_IDU_Kode_PT,'') like ':6' and (DocType = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') and (ISNULL(NumAtCard,'') like '%'+ISNULL(':8','')+'%') and CANCELED <> 'C' :9 :10 :11

SQL_STMT_U.val: select DocEntry, ObjType,docStatus,canceled,finncpriod from orpc WITH (NOLOCK) where (CardCode = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') and (DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and ISNULL(U_IDU_Kode_PT,'') like ':6' and (DocType = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') and (ISNULL(NumAtCard,'') like '%'+ISNULL(':8','')+'%') and CANCELED <> 'C' :9 :10 :11 order by DocEntry Desc

select T0.DocDate as 'Posting Date' ,T0.DocNum as 'Document Number' , T0.CardName as 'Supplier Name' , TRIM(REPLACE(T0.numatcard,char(59),' ')) as 'Supplier Reference' , T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee' , T0.DocCur as 'Currency' , T1.Dscription as 'Item Name' , T1.U_IDU_QtyPack as 'Qty Pack' , T1.U_IDU_UOMPack as 'UOM Pack' , T1.Quantity as 'Qty' , T1.unitMsr as 'UOM Qty' , T1.Price as 'Price' , T1.LineTotal as 'SubTotal' , T1.Vatsum as 'Total PPn' , T0.doctotal as 'Total CN' , Trim(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(T0.comments,char(13),' '),char(10),' '),Char(59),' ')) as 'Remarks' , T0.DocStatus as 'Status' , T1.basetype as 'Base Document' , T1.baseref as 'Base Number' , T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from ORPC T0 join RPC1 T1 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry where (T0.CardCode = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and T0.datasource = 'S' and DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and ISNULL(T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT,'') like ':6' and (T0.DocType = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') and (ISNULL(T0.NumAtCard,'') like '%'+ISNULL(':8','')+'%') and T0.CANCELED <> 'C' :9 :10 :11 order by T0.DocEntry Desc
